BOTULISM, BREAD PRODUCTS - CANADA: RECALL
***************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
ProMED-mail, a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
<http://www.isid.org>
See Also
Botulism advisory, beef jerky - Canada (N.S.): recall 20010217.0313
